---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="Meet Zak Winnick, your Fora travel advisor specializing in premium travel experiences, luxury hotels, and curated itineraries."
>
  <!-- Dark Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-charcoal-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-center min-h-[60vh]">
        <div class="lg:col-span-6 order-2 lg:order-1">
          <img
            src="/zakfull-vasquez.jpg"
            alt="Zak Winnick"
            class="w-full max-w-lg mx-auto lg:max-w-none aspect-video object-cover object-center"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-6 order-1 lg:order-2">
          <p class="font-sans text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-6 text-terracotta-500">
            Certified Fora Travel Advisor
          </p>
          <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl xl:text-8xl font-display font-medium leading-[0.95] tracking-tight text-cream-50">
            Zak<br />
            <span class="text-terracotta-500">Winnick</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-display leading-relaxed text-cream-200 mt-8 max-w-lg">
            Hotels you'll brag about. The intel to make it happen.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full h-px bg-charcoal-700"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- Personal Story Section -->
  <section class="bg-cream-100 dark:bg-forest-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <!-- Left Column - Narrow -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-4">
          <p class="font-sans text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4 text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">
            Background
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-medium mb-8 text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">
            A path less<br />conventional
          </h2>
          <div class="w-16 h-px mb-8 bg-terracotta-500 dark:bg-amber-400"></div>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-2 text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">Background</p>
              <p class="font-display text-lg text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">Luxury Hospitality</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-2 text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">Experience</p>
              <p class="font-display text-lg text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">15+ Years</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Column - Wide -->
        <div class="lg:col-span-8 lg:pt-16">
          <div class="space-y-8 max-w-2xl text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
              I spent fifteen years working inside some of the best hotels in the country, including the Wynn Las Vegas, the Cosmopolitan of Las Vegas, and the Grand Hyatt Nashville. I've worked front of house checking in guests and behind the scenes keeping operations running. I've seen what it takes to deliver a genuinely great stay, and I've seen what happens when properties decide their reputation will do the work for them.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
              Working in luxury hospitality changes how you evaluate a hotel. You stop looking at the marketing and start paying attention to the things that actually matter: how the staff responds when something goes wrong, whether the property invests in the details guests don't consciously notice, and if the experience matches what you were promised when you booked. After years of watching this from the inside, I developed a standard for what I think a great stay should look like. <span class="text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">I won't book a client into a property I wouldn't stay at myself.</span>
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
              That philosophy is why I became a travel advisor. Not to forward confirmation emails and technically be helpful, but to help clients find hotels that actually deserve their money. I focus on boutique hotels, luxury resorts, and thoughtfully built itineraries where having someone in your corner makes a real difference. I work with properties where I can get you something you wouldn't get booking on your own: room upgrades, resort credits, early check-in, the table at the restaurant you couldn't get into.
            </p>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
              My standards are high because I've seen what's possible when a hotel gets it right. I like helping my clients experience that too.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy Section -->
  <section class="bg-cream-50 dark:bg-forest-950">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="text-center mb-20">
        <p class="font-sans text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-8 text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">
          Philosophy
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-7xl font-display font-medium leading-[1.1] max-w-5xl mx-auto text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">
          Turning <span class="text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">your vision</span> into trips worth bragging about
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-px bg-charcoal-200 dark:bg-forest-700">
        <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 bg-cream-50 dark:bg-forest-950 transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <span class="text-6xl font-display font-medium text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">01</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-medium mt-6 mb-4 text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">The Right Room</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">
            Not just any room. The room. Corner suite, best view, upgrade already confirmed. The details that make a difference.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 bg-cream-50 dark:bg-forest-950 transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <span class="text-6xl font-display font-medium text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">02</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-medium mt-6 mb-4 text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">Access, Not Availability</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">
            The reservation that's "fully booked." The experience that's not on the website. Doors open when you know who to ask.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 bg-cream-50 dark:bg-forest-950 transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <span class="text-6xl font-display font-medium text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">03</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-display font-medium mt-6 mb-4 text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">Curated, Not Generic</h3>
          <p class="leading-relaxed text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">
            Your trip should feel like yours, not a template with your name on it. Every itinerary designed around how you want to travel.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Drives Me Section -->
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-forest-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        <div>
          <p class="font-sans text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-6 text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">
            What Drives Me
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-medium leading-tight mb-8 text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">
            Finding the places<br />
            <span class="text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">worth finding</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8 text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">
            I've built my career around understanding what makes a travel experience memorable. It's not about the most expensive option. It's about the right one. The boutique hotel with the story. The restaurant the locals actually go to. The view that doesn't show up on the first page of search results.
          </p>
          <div class="w-full h-px mb-8 bg-charcoal-200 dark:bg-forest-700"></div>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">
            When I'm not planning trips for clients, I'm out traveling. Testing properties, building relationships, discovering the details that separate "nice" from "I can't believe you found this place."
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="p-6 lg:p-8 bg-cream-50 dark:bg-forest-950 border border-charcoal-200 dark:border-forest-700 transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <span class="text-3xl font-display text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">01</span>
            <p class="text-lg font-display mt-4 text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">Hotels & Resorts</p>
            <p class="text-sm mt-2 text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">The ones worth staying at</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 lg:p-8 bg-cream-50 dark:bg-forest-950 border border-charcoal-200 dark:border-forest-700 transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <span class="text-3xl font-display text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">02</span>
            <p class="text-lg font-display mt-4 text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">Dining</p>
            <p class="text-sm mt-2 text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">Beyond the guidebooks</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 lg:p-8 bg-cream-50 dark:bg-forest-950 border border-charcoal-200 dark:border-forest-700 transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <span class="text-3xl font-display text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">03</span>
            <p class="text-lg font-display mt-4 text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">Experiences</p>
            <p class="text-sm mt-2 text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">Not on the website</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 lg:p-8 bg-cream-50 dark:bg-forest-950 border border-charcoal-200 dark:border-forest-700 transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
            <span class="text-3xl font-display text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">04</span>
            <p class="text-lg font-display mt-4 text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">Destinations</p>
            <p class="text-sm mt-2 text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">Chosen with intention</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Fora Credentials Section -->
  <section class="bg-cream-50 dark:bg-forest-950">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-5">
          <p class="font-sans text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-6 text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">
            Credentials
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-display font-medium leading-tight text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">
            Certified<br />
            <span class="text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">Fora</span> Travel<br />
            Advisor
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="lg:col-span-7 lg:pt-8">
          <div class="p-8 lg:p-12 bg-cream-100 dark:bg-forest-900 border border-charcoal-200 dark:border-forest-700">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-6 mb-8">
              <div class="w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 bg-terracotta-500 dark:bg-amber-400">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-cream-50 dark:text-forest-950" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.15em] uppercase mb-2 text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">Partnership</p>
                <p class="text-xl font-display font-medium text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">Fora Travel</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-6 text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">
              <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
                I partnered with Fora because they share my belief that travel should be personal, not transactional. Their platform provides the tools and relationships to deliver exceptional experiences while maintaining the personal touch that makes travel planning meaningful.
              </p>
              <p class="leading-relaxed">
                As a Fora advisor, I have access to exclusive perks, upgrades, and insider knowledge that transform your trip, from complimentary breakfast and room upgrades to special amenities and VIP treatment.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-charcoal-200 dark:border-forest-700">
              <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                <div>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-display font-medium text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">Exclusive</p>
                  <p class="text-sm mt-1 text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">Hotel Perks</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-display font-medium text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">VIP</p>
                  <p class="text-sm mt-1 text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">Treatment</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="text-2xl font-display font-medium text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">Insider</p>
                  <p class="text-sm mt-1 text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">Knowledge</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quote Section -->
  <section class="bg-cream-100 dark:bg-forest-900">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32 text-center">
      <blockquote>
        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-display font-medium leading-relaxed mb-8 text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">
          "The best trips aren't about checking boxes. They're about finding those
          <span class="text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">unexpected moments</span>
          that stay with you long after you've unpacked."
        </p>
        <footer>
          <div class="w-12 h-px mx-auto mb-6 bg-terracotta-500 dark:bg-amber-400"></div>
          <cite class="not-italic font-sans text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">
            Zak Winnick
          </cite>
        </footer>
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="bg-cream-50 dark:bg-forest-950">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 py-16 md:py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <p class="font-sans text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-6 text-terracotta-500 dark:text-amber-400">
          Start Planning
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-display font-medium leading-tight mb-8 text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50">
          Ready to plan something worth taking?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 text-charcoal-600 dark:text-cream-200">
          Tell me where you want to go. Or just tell me what you're in the mood for. Either way, we'll figure it out together.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center">
          <a
            href={`${baseUrl}contact`}
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 font-sans text-sm tracking-[0.1em] uppercase bg-terracotta-500 dark:bg-amber-400 text-cream-50 dark:text-forest-950 border border-terracotta-500 dark:border-amber-400 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-terracotta-600 dark:hover:bg-amber-500"
          >
            Let's Talk
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href={`${baseUrl}services`}
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 font-sans text-sm tracking-[0.1em] uppercase bg-transparent text-charcoal-900 dark:text-cream-50 border border-charcoal-900 dark:border-cream-50 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-charcoal-900 dark:hover:bg-cream-50 hover:text-cream-50 dark:hover:text-forest-950"
          >
            View Services
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
